snippet.textDisplay: I like the fact that she's holding a microphone without foam/ no popfilter onto a windy stage, and that you can't even hear the wind through the microphone. Not a single breath. Better yet: if you check the comments, you will see that these women actually feel empowered by a performance like this. It's female empowerment by style over substance.
